### Data and Word Lists

The toxicity detection word lists included in this software are compiled from various public sources and are provided for content moderation purposes only. These lists:

- Are intended for automated content filtering applications
- Should be used in conjunction with human review
- May contain words that could be offensive when viewed out of context
- Are provided "as is" without warranty of completeness or accuracy
- Should be customized based on your specific use case and jurisdiction

